          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"7-temporal-difference\">\u7b2c 7 \u7ae0 \u00b7 \u65f6\u5e8f\u5dee\u5206\u65b9\u6cd5 (Temporal-Difference)</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">TD = <strong>\u8499\u7279\u5361\u6d1b\u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u7248</strong> + <strong>\u968f\u673a\u8fd1\u4f3c\u7684\u5e94\u7528</strong>\uff1a\u4e0d\u5fc5\u7b49 episode \u7ed3\u675f\uff0c\n\u6bcf\u8d70\u4e00\u6b65\u5c31\u7528<strong>\u81ea\u4e3e (bootstrapping)</strong> \u66f4\u65b0\u2014\u2014\u7528\"\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u7684\u4f30\u8ba1\"\u6539\u8fdb\"\u5f53\u524d\u4f30\u8ba1\"\u3002</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">\u7edf\u4e00\u5f62\u5f0f\uff1a\u65b0\u4f30\u8ba1 \u2190 \u65e7\u4f30\u8ba1 + \u03b1\u00b7[ TD target \u2212 \u65e7\u4f30\u8ba1 ]</span>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>\u7b97\u6cd5</th>\n<th>\u5b66\u4ec0\u4e48</th>\n<th>TD target</th>\n<th>\u7528\u9014</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>TD(0)</strong></td>\n<td><marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(v_\\pi(s)||)</marimo-tex></td>\n<td><marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(r+\\gamma v(s')||)</marimo-tex></td>\n<td>\u8bc4\u4f30\u7ed9\u5b9a\u7b56\u7565</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Sarsa</strong></td>\n<td><marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(q_\\pi(s,a)||)</marimo-tex></td>\n<td><marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(r+\\gamma q(s',a')||)</marimo-tex></td>\n<td>on-policy \u63a7\u5236</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Expected Sarsa</strong></td>\n<td><marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(q_\\pi||)</marimo-tex></td>\n<td><marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(r+ \\gamma \\sum_{a'}\\pi(a'\\|s')q(s',a')||)</marimo-tex></td>\n<td>\u65b9\u5dee\u66f4\u5c0f</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Q-learning</strong></td>\n<td><marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(q^*(s,a)||)</marimo-tex></td>\n<td><marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(r+\\gamma\\max_{a'}q(s',a')||)</marimo-tex></td>\n<td>off-policy \u63a7\u5236</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">\u672c\u7ae0\u91cd\u70b9\uff1a\u7528<strong>\u9010\u6b65\u56de\u653e\u6ed1\u5757</strong>\u770b Q-learning \u7684\u7b56\u7565\u5982\u4f55\u4ece\u6df7\u4e71<strong>\u5b66</strong>\u5230\u6700\u4f18\uff1b\n\u518d\u7528<strong>\u53c2\u6570\u6ed1\u5757 + \u8bad\u7ec3\u6309\u94ae</strong>\u4eb2\u624b\u8c03 \u03b1\u3001\u03b5\uff0c\u770b\u5bf9\u7ed3\u679c\u7684\u5f71\u54cd\u3002</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
